WEBVTT

00:43.043 --> 00:45.337
The alien expert is in.

00:47.130 --> 00:48.715
Time to get to work.

00:48.799 --> 00:50.717
As Carl Sagan once said,

00:50.801 --> 00:54.555
"Extraordinary claims
require extraordinary evidence."

00:55.097 --> 00:58.058
Sorry you didn't get sent into space,
RoboSimian.

00:58.141 --> 01:00.853
But you can still have
plenty of fun here with us.
